  "body": "**üßê Motivation**\r\nMy contracts work with ERC20 stablecoin contracts as a currencies, and sometime I need to make a conversion say USDT to USDC\r\nIn this case I need to work with decimals from contracts while I do convertaion, so I need to get decimals from those contracts, and I would like to do that by IERC20 interface.\r\n\r\n**üìù Details**\r\nMake IERC20 (interface) support of ```decimals()```, to get ability to get decimals from erc20 token contracts, using only their interface IERC20 contract\r\n\r\n<!-- Make sure that you have reviewed the OpenZeppelin Contracts Contributor Guidelines. -->\r\n<!-- https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md -->\r\n",
